<br><br>

<span style="font-weight: bold">2016 January 10: &nbsp;&nbsp;New 6th dan</span><br>
<span style="line-height: 22px; font-size: 20px; color: red;">(THIS EVENT IS CONCLUDED. ALL MATERIALS RELATING TO IT ARE RETAINED FOR ARCHIVING PURPOSES ONLY.)</span><br><br><br>


We congratulate Sensei Giovanni Capannelli on his promotion to roku-dan. He was promoted at the 2016 Kagami Biraki at Hombu Dojo in Tokyo. Giovanni teaches the early morning T-Th class at MAC.<br><br>

We also congratulate Sensei Oscar Mistula on being promoted to roku-dan at the same Kagami Biraki. Oscar trains and teaches in Sydney, Australia. He hails from Cagayan de Oro City.<br><br>


